    <p>{`The Events APIs cannot be used for any purpose other than triggering, acknowledging, or resolving PagerDuty incidents. It uses 32-character integration keys that cannot be used with the REST API, so it is safe to store these API keys in monitoring systems and other tools without fear that they can be used to gain access to sensitive data in your account.`}</p>
